moji\" /> <br />\n一開始我會當佢係屋企人咁，但成日郁啲就講分手已經唔夠膽當佢係屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我只係知道屋企人唔會離我而去而佢會<br />\n我好後悔去左溝個靚女，都係嗰句自己揀仆左街放工返到去都冇得喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n珍惜你地儲到錢，有自由時間可以屋企攤一日嘅日子。。。9up完</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70cbee6569ba58e40e20395d7736f414faf3ec0d","tid":450603,"uid":42314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T14:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b3b0717315a347be0a02c2a1666a6e71ab368b2","tid":450603,"uid":155999,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T15:32:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好矛盾 單身個陣就想有女朋友 <br />\n<br />\n到拍左一陣 又會覺得單身個陣一個人靜靜地都幾好 唔洗同對方交代任何野 無交嘈 多左時間用 慳左錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人又係咁矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n可能你已經唔愛佢或者懶得愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ac4b9aeb4345f6a2c865d9043c9ee12d29e02a","tid":450603,"uid":155999,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T15:59:46.000Z","msg":"你想既時候就唔覺得攰，錢用得值，唔想既時候就食個飯都覺得攰，洗左好多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但現實拍拖冇得你永遠都想"},{"pid":"6e90314cda84b23795185d7852afed25758b8a15","tid":450603,"uid":42314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T16:38:22.000Z",